            <thetext>This code works in source form, but not when doing the final build (tested with FF 3.6, Chrome and Safari 4 on a Mac):

var elem = document.getElementById(&quot;elem&quot;);
qx.event.Registration.addListener(elem, &quot;change&quot;, function() {});

I had to change it to:

